r class for CodeInterpreterClient with upload and run methods\n968: - **Container pattern**: uv base image, vendored SDK, PYTHONPATH=/app\n969: - **K8s deployment**: Secret for API key, env for AgentCube URLs\n970: - **Test strategy**: Mock SDK client, TestClient for FastAPI, integration tests require live backend\n971: \n972: ---\n973: \n974: ## Implementation Timeline\n975: \n976: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n977: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n978: | Phase 1: Directory Structure | T1.1-T1.6 | Pending | 0% |\n979: | Phase 2: Plugin Entry Point | T2.1-T2.3 | Pending | 0% |\n980: | Phase 3: Plugin Manifest | T3.1-T3.8 | Pending | 0% |\n981: | Phase 4: Provider Descriptor | T4.1-T4.4 | Pending | 0% |\n982: | Phase 5: Provider Implementation | T5.1-T5.4 | Pending | 0% |\n983: | Phase 6: Tool Schema | T6.1-T6.11 | Pending | 0% |\n984: | Phase 7: Tool Implementation | T7.1-T7.11 | Pending | 0% |\n985: | Phase 8: Plugin Dependencies | T8.1-T8.3 | Pending | 0% |\n986: | Phase 9: Plugin Documentation | T9.1-T9.4 | Pending | 0% |\n\n(Output capped at 50 KB. Showing lines 1-986. Use offset=987 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-036 — Dify 插件集成 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-036 — Dify 插件集成 |\n| Module | integrations |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Dify Plugin Directory Structure (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create `integrations/dify-plugin/` directory\n  - Purpose: Initialize plugin package root","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-036/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775893391396,"end":1775893391419}}}}
